like serious fascism was on the rise and Nazism was on the rise in Europe.

221
00:13:59,819 --> 00:14:03,959
And there was a big like fascist Nazi movement here in London and in the UK.

222
00:14:04,400 --> 00:14:07,120
And there was a march, the fascist march in London.

223
00:14:07,699 --> 00:14:10,180
And the locals in East London came out and they didn't accept it.

224
00:14:10,620 --> 00:14:11,560
There was a massive fire.

225
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:15,020
There's a big mural down the street, which is nice.

226
00:14:15,020 --> 00:14:16,520
If you're ever in London, go check it out.

227
00:14:17,319 --> 00:14:20,400
And I go there, I cycle past it all the time and quite often I will stop and just have

228
00:14:20,400 --> 00:14:20,860
a little look.

229
00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:24,819
And I stopped there the other day and I was standing by this mural and I was looking at

230
00:14:24,819 --> 00:14:25,220
this mural.

231
00:14:26,500 --> 00:14:29,880
And just as I was thinking, it was summer's going down, painting the scene.

232
00:14:30,660 --> 00:14:41,260
And just as I was looking at it, I saw that somebody had put a sticker right on the railing

233
00:14:41,260 --> 00:14:42,120
at the bottom, right in the middle.

234
00:14:42,120 --> 00:14:44,700
A big tax world not work sticker.

235
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:19,240
And when I see stuff like that, it makes me think that all the hard work is worth it.

236
00:15:22,420 --> 00:15:23,080
So that's it.

237
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:23,580
