00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,840
We're trying to do some really exciting stuff.

242
00:15:36,120 --> 00:15:37,000
So many offers coming in.

243
00:15:37,060 --> 00:15:38,360
We're trying to do some good stuff.

244
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:42,900
Touring Italy, which is happening now, you'll have probably missed it by the time this comes

